data.description: This cute, cozy cottage sits on an oversized lot giving you lots of options. The extra acreage potentially could be room for expansion, a pool or just room to roam. The picket fence is newly painted white and adds to the curb appeal. A charming covered front porch welcomes you home and makes a great first impression for your neighbors and guests. The home features an open family to dining room with wood-like floors and updated colors. The kitchen has been remodeled with all the latest upgrades. At one end of the kitchen is an eat-in nook or sunroom and room for your stackable washer and dryer. 3 bedrooms with hall bath completes the interior layout. The property includes the wooded portion to the right of the house and storage shed.
